View Member's: Reviews I ordered six cartridges from printerinks on 22nd March. When they still hadn't arrived after a week I rang them & was told they would be redispatched. I have yet to receive them oer two weeks after the order.I have tried around 10 times to phone them - each time being on hold for over 10 miniutes but unable to get through.I have tried e-mailing them & can get no response. They are quite happy to take my money & not provide my products. I am so frustrated with them I cannot describe it.My advice would be to order elsewhere. Overall Rating
